◆ dlb_event_sched_t

enum dlb_event_sched_t

Event Scheduling Types.

Enumerator
SCHED_ATOMIC 

Atomic scheduling. Only valid if the destination queue is load-balanced.

SCHED_UNORDERED 

Unordered scheduling. Only valid if the destination queue is load-balanced and was configured with zero sequence numbers.

SCHED_ORDERED 

Ordered scheduling. Only valid if the destination queue is load-balanced and was configured with non-zero sequence numbers.

SCHED_DIRECTED 

Directed scheduling. Only valid when the destination queue is directed.
